room_title: Escape room "The Conjuring" by Panic Escape Room in Chicago
room_address: 990 Grand Canyon Pkwy Hoffman Estates, IL 60169
room_description: A desperate cry for help falls on deaf ears as you and your group take up the challenge to save this poor girl. Your journey begins in the infamous Warren’s Occult museum as you search for clues as to what was taken and what has caused the neighbors to abandon their home after there young daughter vanished. Remember everything in the Warren’s is possessed or cursed so avoid taking anything with you!
